msgstr ""

#. module: libraries
#: model_terms:product.template,description:libraries.product_product_19_product_template
msgid ""
"The worlds of celebrity and sports are brilliantly dissected and turned "
"upside down in #1 New York Times bestselling author Harlan Coben’s debut "
"thriller.Theirs was a marriage made in tabloid heaven, but no sooner had "
"supermodel Laura Ayars and Celtics star David Baskin said “I do” than "
"tragedy struck. While honeymooning on Australia’s Great Barrier Reef, David "
"went out for a swim—and never returned.Now widowed and grieving, Laura has a"
